ype": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "27_1724566373.695544", "card_id": "Q_665121217", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 50}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "职场新人，前辈们都告诉我要耐得住，成长需要时间，但我想快速独当一面，可行吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-8c4e8e1b5b13550ab21dc92455728e66_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "19 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/665121217"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ivrzl8J/56cobEAMaCTExMDA4MjI1MSC7tqK2BjAAOFdAG3IJNjY1MTIxMjE3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "28_1724566373.695714", "card_id": "Q_657505913", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 20}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "白居易有哪些难以理解的诗句？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-109715cd2e3fd11b9fff78d63eeb05c4_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "18 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/657505913"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ivrzl8J/56cobEAMaCTEwODM5MDE5NyDKrtmyBjAAODdAHHIJNjU3NTA1OTEzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "29_1724566373.695876", "card_id": "Q_664891821", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 46}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "抑郁是一种怎样的感受？正在被抑郁症「拉扯」的人真正想听到的话是什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "7 月，我来到一个专门面向抑郁症家庭的夏令营，来之前，我特别想搞清楚的一个问题是，「抑郁那一刻是如何发生的？」 在这里，有孩子告诉我，当时是没法呼吸的，「像把我团成一个团，锁在一个箱子里面，一点一点把箱子里的空气抽出去，心脏怦怦不停地跳，不停地跳。」 另一个男孩告诉我，发现自己得病的那一刻，「很恐慌很恐慌，因为你完全不知道这个东西是怎么产生的。」 「这东西」，是什么？我问他。 男孩说——「这东西」就是一些很复杂很奇怪的幻想，想到自己突然有一天拿把手枪，和敌国特工做周旋。这个场景过后，这个特工的故事会往下续写，又或者马上跳跃到另一个故事，比如一个售票员的故事。 「就是你日常生活中可能根本不会发生的场景，在你脑海里，不停地上演。」 当一个人陷入抑郁的时候，会经历一系列情绪、行为和身体上的变化。这到底是一种怎样的感受？ 正在被抑郁症「拉扯」的人，需要哪些支持？真正想听到的话是什么？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-d5bc66167a1bc8efd9b08f0de45f1492_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "16 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/664891821"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ivrzl8J/56cobEAMaCTExMDAzMTI4MCCuvpa2BjAAODhAHXIJNjY0ODkxODIxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}], "paging": {"is_end": true, "is_start": false, "next": "", "previous": "", "totals": 0}, "fresh_text": "热榜已更新", "display_num": 15, "display_first": true, "fb_bill_main_rise": 0, "head_zone": {"type": "billboard_lantern", "data": [{"id": "1724871100431802368", "link_url": "https://www.zhihu.com/appview/community_construction", "title": "辟谣专区", "source_type": 0, "attached_info": "Ci4QABoTMTcyNDg3MTEwMDQzMTgwMjM2OHITMTcyNDg3MTEwMDQzMTgwMjM2OHgA", "tag": "辟谣", "tag_bg_color": "GRD01A"}]}}